room_title: Escape room "Apollo 920: Space Mission" by Locked Inside Room Escape in Melbourne
room_description: The American Flag is missing from the moon and the objective of the Apollo 920 Space Mission is to get it back. Before you route to the moon, you and your team of astronauts are headed to the International Space Station for supplies when you receive an emergency transmission from Houston - there is a strange distress signal coming from the ISS and it is off the computed trajectory. You are approaching the ISS far ahead of schedule and are going too fast, risking a collision! You and your team must find a way to override the autopilot and dock safely before your 60 minutes to impact.
